Interface RadioGroup.OnCheckedChangeListener

  • Enclosing class:
    RadioGroup

    public static interface RadioGroup.OnCheckedChangeListener

    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when the checked radio button changed in this group.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onCheckedChanged(RadioGroup group, int checkedId)
      Called when the checked radio button has changed.

    • Method Detail

      • onCheckedChanged

        void onCheckedChanged(RadioGroup group,
                      int checkedId)

        Called when the checked radio button has changed. When the selection is cleared, checkedId is -1.

        Parameters:
        group - the group in which the checked radio button has changed
        checkedId - the unique identifier of the newly checked radio button
